message.body: That's what we going to do to Anna? Like a star instead of a halo?
You got it all wrong friend. That is what anna and i are going to do to you
That's what you guys want to do to me... Unfortunately it's too hard to get me to stop talking about myself, I'll talk and talk and there won't be a moment for any of that...
Hahahaha. I will remember the duct tape
Well I'm glad you think of me when you see women getting roughed up. It cracks me up.
Dont take it as that big of a compliment. It makes me think of all women
Not a compliment in the least. But it is mighty funny how ironic it is
